		<title>What Statisticians Want to Know about Causal Inference and The Book of Why</title>
		<link>https://causality.cs.ucla.edu/blog/index.php/2020/05/31/what-statisticians-want-to-know-about-causal-inference-and-the-book-of-why/</link>
